            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1681827826559-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once slightly softened, add 380ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[500ml]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [650ml] </span><strong>boiled water </strong>to the pan with your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong></p><p>Stir everything together and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling reduce the heat to medium and cook, covered, for 10-12 min or until the potatoes are fork tender – this is your <strong>chowder base</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1681827831502-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1681827831502-x400.jpg",
